slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528157378282be0071308096951bfdb165b6aabe","tid":1390973,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"我哋由612開始爭取成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n不過，我哋從來冇討論過委員會由咩人去組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人分析琴日中共為成立獨立調查委員會開綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係時候開始討論當中嘅細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過有法官判示威者以胸部襲警後，相信大家都明白香港有好多紅底法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以獨立調查委員會一定唔可以只係有本地法官組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要嘅獨立調查委員會係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>由國際專家、聯合國，甚至海牙軍事法庭嘅人組成</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拒絕港共自己人查自己人<br />\n<br />\n要由國際專家調查事件</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13caa9dfc83e33ec3578ec05335490fe5749673","tid":1390973,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"［廣傳］ 有咩人組成獨立調查委員會？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e63226b610fad94575ff9452040093c2c714b25c","tid":1390973,"uid":200026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0